title: Fantastic one bedroom loft apartment in Minneapolis
posting_body: ['Kari Anderson and REI Real Estate & Property Management are excited to present this fantastic loft apartment in the Prospect Park neighborhood of Minneapolis.', 'Upon entering the apartment, you will first notice that the ceilings are 18 feet tall.', 'This creates the feeling that you get in an older building, but it has been updated and remodeled beautifully.', 'There is a balanced mix of concrete, windows, modern appliances and authentic exposed brick.', 'There are just over 1100 square feet!', 'The bedroom area is huge and it also has a nice sized walk-in closet.', 'The bathroom is also very spacious.', 'For your convenience, you will also enjoy having your own washer and dryer.', 'The kitchen has beautiful updates along with stainless steel appliances.', 'The dining area and living room are located toward the front of the unit and the entire place has a very open feeling.', 'The windows are wonderful and offer tons of natural light.', 'The roof of the building has stunning views and there are also lots of chairs, tables, fire pits and grills available for you to use.', 'This apartment also has a designated storage unit and underground parking space.', "The property's location offers a lot of perks, including trails, parks, transportation options, shopping and restaurants.", 'The tenant is responsible for the electricity.', 'Gas, heat, water, sewer and trash are covered!', 'Pets to be considered along with an additional pet deposit.', 'Call or text Kari Anderson at', 'show contact info', 'if you have any questions or if you would like to request a showing.', 'For additional rentals and information about our property management, please see <URL>.']
